{"tid":1447234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【同是天涯香港人】菲律賓人質事件vs今日香港","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T05:07:19.000Z","uid":242050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45726cf69bbcd5d0802fa609a6f9b12b2d10d5e8","tid":1447234,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XgMcD19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXgMcD19.jpg&h=610fc04f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九年前的八月，突如其來的新聞，一個大家都不想發生的悲劇：2010年8月的那一天，每個香港人也在電視機旁邊看著直播，多小時的煎熬，最後傳來不幸的消息，事後大家都在指責菲律賓警察的無能，不然傷亡一定能夠減低。<br />\n<br />\n九年後的八月，香港警察終於顯示出他們的威力，可是他們槍頭指著的，是香港市民。本來保護香港市民的團隊，正正就是那些警察，無差別的發放橡膠子彈及催淚彈、拘捕市民。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>痛心</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a9eb6d8f55899ca0ce89b32a3e9e53220e2b7896","tid":1447234,"uid":199816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:49:36.000Z","msg":"集體PM民陣發起大遊行<br />\n<br />\n和理非大遊行"},{"pid":"7c767561f5dd0764135ea72bd58a4b98245c9b30","tid":1447234,"uid":222513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:07:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1492907/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1492907/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n823 除咗係人鏈, 仲係港人之痛馬尼拉人質事件,唔好忘記大陸對此事嘅冷血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}